water boyy is a 2015 thai lgbt drama film directed by rachi kusonkusiri and starring luangsodsai anupart , nappon gomarachun and beam papangkorn . it was filmed primarily in thailand . in early march , it was revealed that there will be a remake named : waterboyy : the series with different actors . new characters are added including phumphothingam nawat and thitipoom techaapaikhun . it started airing on april 9 , 2017 .